ingredients: basmati rice, water, ghee, cinnamon stick, green cardamom pods, cloves, bay leaf, salt
cooking_instructions: 1. Wash the rice and soak it in water for 30 minutes. 2. In a large saucepan, heat ghee and add whole spices - cinnamon stick, green cardamom pods, cloves, and bay leaf. 3. Drain the soaked rice and add it to the saucepan. Stir to coat with ghee and spices. 4. Add water and salt. 5. Bring to a boil, then simmer until the rice is tender. 6. Fluff the rice before serving.

ingredients: chicken, rice flour, cornstarch, ginger-garlic paste, soy sauce, red chili flakes, vegetable oil, onion, bell peppers, green chili peppers, fresh cilantro leaves
cooking_instructions: 1. In a bowl, mix chicken with rice flour, cornstarch, ginger-garlic paste, soy sauce, and red chili flakes. 2. Stir in green chili peppers and cook for a minute. 5. Garnish with fresh cilantro leaves before serving.

ingredients: rice vermicelli, vegetable oil, mustard seeds, cumin seeds, urad dal, chana dal, dried red chili peppers, curry leaves, onion, green beans, carrot, green peas, turmeric powder, salt, fresh cilantro leaves
cooking_instructions: 1. Cook rice vermicelli according to package instructions, drain, and set aside. 2. ingredients: chickpea flour, vegetable oil, mustard seeds, cumin seeds, urad dal, chana dal, dried red chili peppers, asafoetida, fresh curry leaves, ginger, green chili peppers, turmeric powder, salt, fresh cilantro leaves
cooking_instructions: 1. In a pan, heat vegetable oil and add mustard seeds, cumin seeds, urad dal, chana dal, dried red chili peppers, asafoetida, and fresh curry leaves. ingredients: rice, lentils, vegetable oil, mustard seeds, cumin seeds, urad dal, chana dal, dried red chili peppers, asafoetida, fresh curry leaves, ginger, turmeric powder, salt, fresh cilantro leaves
